OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,FEmma Aspinall told ITV's Rob Smith how
OL,7,Fshe taught infant swim survival
OL,8,Flessons in Wigan for years, until the
OL,9,Fpool she was using closed down
OL,11,FA mum who learned to teach a
OL,12,Fcontroversial swim survival technique
OL,13,Fafter her son drowned in an accident,
OL,14,Fsays she is struggling to find a pool
OL,15,Fto continue her lessons.
OL,17,FEmma Aspinall, from Wigan, lost her
OL,18,Fson Loui in 2013 after he wandered
OL,19,Finto a pool without being seen, while
OL,20,Fon holiday in Tunisia, and never came
OL,21,Fback out.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,FAfter Loui's death, Emma travelled to
OL,7,FAmerica to train in infant survival
OL,8,Fswimming and taught hundreds of
OL,9,Fchildren to "self rescue" until the
OL,10,Fvenue she was using closed three years
OL,11,Fago. She then took a break to have a
OL,12,Fbaby.
OL,14,FBut she has been unable to find a
OL,15,Freplacement pool ever since, with
OL,16,Frising running costs forcing many to
OL,17,Fshut. She also fears that controversy
OL,18,Faround the technique may hinder her
OL,19,Fsearch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,F"The main reason why we're doing it is
OL,7,Fto try and prevent other families
OL,8,Fgoing through what we've gone
OL,9,Fthrough," she said.
OL,11,F"It took a lot for us to get started,
OL,12,Fto get the training, to get the
OL,13,Flessons over here in England.
OL,15,F"And then for it to just come to an
OL,16,Fend, it's gutting really."
OL,18,FEmma added that the rising costs of
OL,19,Frunning and repairing pools have a
OL,20,F"part to play".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,F"It's not cheap running a pool," she
OL,7,Fadded.
OL,9,F"A lot of pools... they've closed them
OL,10,Ffor that reason because they just
OL,11,Fcan't afford it."
OL,13,FThe method Emma brought to the North
OL,14,FWest, teaches children how to roll
OL,15,Fover onto their back to rest and
OL,16,Fbreathe - before learning any swim
OL,17,Fstrokes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,FA charity which she set up to ensure
OL,7,Fsuch safety lessons are available to
OL,8,Fany child, regardless of their
OL,9,Ffamily's financial situation, say they
OL,10,Fdo not even need an existing pool to
OL,11,Frun their classes.
OL,13,FThe chair of Doit4Loui, Emma Harvey,
OL,14,Ftold ITV News that they just need a
OL,15,Fbuilding they can retrofit to house
OL,16,Fwhat is effectively a "temporary" pool.
OL,18,F"We just need premises or a space,"
OL,19,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,F"We can build a pool on top of floor
OL,7,Flevel.
OL,9,F"It wouldn't be a pool where we would
OL,10,Fbe digging underground, and it's (not)
OL,11,Fa permanent fixture.
OL,13,F"And we will make it look nice around
OL,14,Ftiling, decking, that kind of thing."
OL,16,FThe technique Emma teaches is
OL,17,Fcontroversial, as some safety experts
OL,18,Fbelieve it can be traumatic and
OL,19,Fpotentially affect a child's feelings
OL,20,Ftowards water in later life.
OL,26,@rD@bpmrD@fpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,FITV News asked national body Swim
OL,7,FEngland for its view. It said:
OL,8,F"Swimming is a life-saving skill, but
OL,9,Fit should be taught in a way that
OL,10,Fsupports children's physical,
OL,11,Femotional and cognitive development.
OL,13,F"We encourage all lesson providers to
OL,14,Ffollow the Swim England Learn to Swim
OL,15,FFramework, which is designed to help
OL,16,Fchildren build water confidence
OL,17,Fgradually, in a positive and
OL,18,Fsupportive environment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,F"Our approach focuses not only on
OL,7,Fsafety, but also on ensuring that
OL,8,Fevery child grows up with a lifelong
OL,9,Flove of the water."
OL,11,FEmma believes her lessons can be
OL,12,Fperceived wrongly and that may have an
OL,13,Fimpact when it comes to finding a new
OL,14,Fplace in which to teach.
OL,16,F"The big issue is how people perceive
OL,17,Four lessons," she says.
OL,19,F"They look at little clips shown
OL,20,Fonline, or on telly, and things like
OL,21,Fthat.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,F"They see a little clip of a lesson
OL,7,Fwhere a child might be crying, and
OL,8,Fthen they think that is it - that's
OL,9,Fall we do, we just make children cry.
OL,11,F"It's really not the case at all.
OL,13,F"We've said this over and over again
OL,14,Fabout children crying for different
OL,15,Freasons.
OL,17,F"Seatbelts in cars... children cry -
OL,18,Fthey don't want to put their seatbelt
OL,19,Fon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,F"So do we just leave the seatbelt off?
OL,7,FOr do we make them put the seatbelt on
OL,8,Ffor their safety?
OL,10,F"We do it, don't we."
OL,12,FGrandfather Dave Matthews, from Wigan,
OL,13,Fsays he is "devastated" that the
OL,14,Flessons cannot continue because of
OL,15,Fwhat they did for one of his
OL,16,Fgrandchildren.
OL,18,FHe says his young grandson, Joe, used
OL,19,Fwhat he learned to "self rescue"
OL,20,Fduring a family holiday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,FDave says: "He'd done all the course,
OL,7,Fand so he was quite proficient at it.
OL,9,F"He was walking along the side of the
OL,10,Fpool, missed his footing, and fell in.
OL,12,F"What happened then was the lifeguard
OL,13,Fon the pool went to jump in to him.
OL,15,F"So I said to the lifeguard: 'No -
OL,16,Fleave him a minute.'
OL,18,F"Next thing, (Joe's) on his back and
OL,19,Fhe's floating, and then he comes round
OL,20,Fand then he swims to the side.
OL,26,@zD@NpmzD@Tpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775056271
OL,3,CMum in search for pool to continue
OL,4,Cchildren's swim survival lessons
OL,6,F"So he actually used the thing in a
OL,7,Freal life situation there."
OL,9,FFinding a pool, or finding a space to
OL,10,Finstall one, is now Emma's priority.
OL,12,FShe wants to work with water safety
OL,13,Fgroups, swimming groups and schools,
OL,14,Fto give lifesaving skills to as many
OL,15,Fchildren as possible.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
